Actions on Conservation Activity

To view actions available on the Conservation Activity select the Action option. A list with all actions/groups of actions will be displayed.

The actions depend on the Conservation Activity state. The following Conservation Activity states are possible:

  • In Progress - Active state of the Conservation Activity. All Conservation Activity actions can be performed - create task, create document, etc.
  • Completed and Locked - The Conservation Activity in Completed and Locked state is inactive. Only the permissions of the Conservation Activity,  Reopen and all print and export actions are visible.
